---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sefer HaMidos - Book of Character Traits" description="The comprehensive work on character development and self-improvement based on Rebbe Nachman's teachings">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>Sefer HaMidos</h1>
    <p>ספר המידות</p>
    <a href="/teachings" class="back-link">← Back to Teachings</a>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="description">
        <strong>Sefer HaMidos</strong> (The Book of Traits) is a comprehensive work that catalogs 
        and examines various character traits—both positive and negative—based on Rebbe Nachman's 
        teachings. This invaluable guide provides deep insights into human psychology and offers 
        practical pathways for character improvement. It serves as an essential tool for anyone 
        seeking to refine their personality and grow spiritually.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="positive-midos">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Positive Traits (מידות טובות)</h2>
      <div class="midos-grid">
        <div class="mido-card positive">
          <h3>Faith (אמונה)</h3>
          <p>Complete trust and belief in Hashem</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mido-card positive">
          <h3>Humility (ענוה)</h3>
          <p>Recognizing one's place before Hashem</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mido-card positive">
          <h3>Joy (שמחה)</h3>
          <p>Serving Hashem with happiness</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mido-card positive">
          <h3>Hope (תקווה)</h3>
          <p>Trusting in future redemption</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mido-card positive">
          <h3>Love (אהבה)</h3>
          <p>Love for Hashem and fellow Jews</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mido-card positive">
          <h3>Fear of Heaven (יראת שמים)</h3>
          <p>Revering and honoring Hashem</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="negative-midos">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Traits to Overcome (מידות לתקן)</h2>
      <div class="midos-grid">
        <div class="mido-card negative">
          <h3>Anger (כעס)</h3>
          <p>Controlling and transforming explosive emotions</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mido-card negative">
          <h3>Pride (גאוה)</h3>
          <p>Overcoming haughtiness and self-exaltation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mido-card negative">
          <h3>Sadness (עצב)</h3>
          <p>Lifting oneself from depression and despair</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mido-card negative">
          <h3>Worry (דאגה)</h3>
          <p>Releasing anxiety through trust in Hashem</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mido-card negative">
          <h3>Laziness (עצלות)</h3>
          <p>Finding motivation for spiritual growth</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mido-card negative">
          <h3>Envy (קנאה)</h3>
          <p>Transforming jealousy into contentment</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="quote">
    <div class="container">
      <blockquote>
        <p class="hebrew">כל מידה ומידה יש לה תיקון</p>
        <p>"Every trait has a rectification."</p>
        <cite>— Sefer HaMidos</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="navigation">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>More Teachings</h2>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/teachings/sichos" class="nav-link">← Sichos HaRan</a>
        <a href="/teachings/likutay-eitzos" class="nav-link">Likutay Eitzos →</a>
        <a href="/teachings/shivchay-moharan" class="nav-link">Shivchay Moharan →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #276749 0%, #48bb78 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-hebrew);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid white;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .intro {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #f0fff4;
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
  }

  .positive-midos {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .positive-midos h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #276749;
  }

  .negative-midos {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #f0fff4;
  }

  .negative-midos h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #276749;
  }

  .midos-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .mido-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .mido-card.positive {
    background: white;
    border-left: 4px solid #48bb78;
  }

  .mido-card.negative {
    background: white;
    border-left: 4px solid #e53e3e;
  }

  .mido-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .mido-card.positive h3 {
    color: #276749;
  }

  .mido-card.negative h3 {
    color: #c53030;
  }

  .mido-card p {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .quote {
    background: #276749;
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quote blockquote {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .quote .hebrew {
    font-family: var(--font-hebrew);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .quote p {
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .navigation {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: #f0fff4;
  }

  .navigation h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .nav-link {
    color: #276749;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
